OL,3,CGuernsey's Bailiff to retire this
OL,4,Csummer after 6 years of service
OL,6,FGuernsey's Bailiff Sir Richard McMahon
OL,7,Fwill retire on 31 August, six years
OL,8,Fafter taking his seat in the States
OL,9,FChamber.
OL,11,FThe 64-year-old became Guernsey's 90th
OL,12,FBailiff after succeeding Sir Richard
OL,13,FCollas in 2020.
OL,15,FHis request to retire has been
OL,16,Fapproved by the King after being
OL,17,Fsubmitted to the Lieutenant-Governor.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
