OL,3,CGuernsey's Bailiff to retire this
OL,4,Csummer after 6 years of service
OL,6,FThe Bailiff is Guernsey's senior civic
OL,7,Ffigure and has judicial, ceremonial
OL,8,Fand parliamentary duties. The role
OL,9,Fincludes acting as speaker in the
OL,10,FStates Chamber and sitting as a judge
OL,11,Fin the Royal Court.
OL,13,FSir Richard was sworn in during the
OL,14,FCovid pandemic, with his installation
OL,15,Fat the Royal Court House streamed
OL,16,Fonline because of social distancing
OL,17,Frestrictions.
OL,19,FWho is Sir Richard McMahon?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
