PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778613066
OL,3,CGuernsey's Bailiff to retire this
OL,4,Csummer after 6 years of service
OL,6,FAfter the death of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,7,Fin 2022, Sir Richard said he felt "a
OL,8,Fprofound sense of loss" and described
OL,9,Fthe late Queen as an example of "duty
OL,10,Fand public service".
OL,12,FTwo years later, he played a central
OL,13,Frole in Guernsey's first visit by King
OL,14,FCharles and Queen Camilla since the
OL,15,FKing's accession to the throne.
OL,17,FHis civic duties have also included
OL,18,Flaunching the Bailiff's Disaster
OL,19,FRelief Fund Ukraine Appeal in 2022.
