OL,3,CGuernsey's Bailiff to retire this
OL,4,Csummer after 6 years of service
OL,6,FHe also oversaw the Bailiwick's
OL,7,Fcommemorations of the special 80th
OL,8,FLiberation Day in 2025.
OL,10,FThe appointment of a new Bailiff is
OL,11,Fdone through a formal process
OL,12,Finvolving Guernsey's Lieutenant-
OL,13,FGovernor and the UK's Ministry of
OL,14,FJustice.
OL,16,FNo successor has yet been named.
